org.jsapar.io

Class Converter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsapar.io.Converter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FilterConverter

    public class Converter
extends Object
    Reads buffer using an input schema and writes to another buffer using an output schema. By adding a LineManipulator you are able to make modifications of each line before it is written to the output. The method manipulate() of all added LineManipulators are called for each line that are parsed successfully.
    Author:
    stejon0
    See Also:
    FilterConverter
